    <example type="good" title="Model Retirement — automated decommissioning">
      <description>Decommissioning legacy fraud detection model. Pre-Retirement, Data Retention, Transition, Documentation, Post-Retirement gates.</description>
      <code lang="python"><![CDATA[
def retire_model(model_id: str, replacement_id: str):
    assert model_registry.get_status(replacement_id) == "production"
    archive_path = f"s3://models-archive/{model_id}/"
    model_registry.archive(model_id, archive_path)

    audit_logs = audit_service.export(
        model_id=model_id, format="parquet",
        destination=f"s3://audit-archive/{model_id}/",
    )
    governance_db.update(
        model_id=model_id,
        status="retired",
        retirement_date=datetime.utcnow(),
        replacement_id=replacement_id,
        archive_location=archive_path,
        audit_archive=audit_logs['location'],
    )
    notify_stakeholders(event="model_retirement",
                       model_id=model_id, replacement_id=replacement_id)
    scheduler.schedule(
        task="delete_model_artifacts",
        model_id=model_id,
        execute_at=datetime.utcnow() + timedelta(days=2555),  # 7 years
    )
]]></code>
      <list>
        <item>Pre-Retirement: replacement validated, performance comparison documented, stakeholder sign-off, regulator notification.</item>
        <item>Data Retention: training data archived (7-year retention), model artifacts preserved, decision logs exported, audit trail closed.</item>
        <item>Transition: traffic routing updated, monitoring disabled, alerts decommissioned, API endpoints deprecated (30-day notice).</item>
        <item>Documentation: retirement date, reason, final performance metrics, lessons learned.</item>
        <item>Post-Retirement: 30-day observation, cold-storage archive, inventory updated, governance record closed.</item>
      </list>
    </example>

    <section name="audit-log-schema">
      <p>Append-only audit table. Use a BEFORE UPDATE trigger that raises an exception so the table is effectively immutable.</p>
      <code lang="sql"><![CDATA[
CREATE TABLE ai_decision_audit (
    -- Identifiers
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    trace_id UUID NOT NULL,
    model_id VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    model_version VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,

    -- Timestamps (UTC always)
    created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW(),
    inference_started_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE,
    inference_completed_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE,

    -- Request context
    request_id VARCHAR(100),
    session_id VARCHAR(100),
    user_id VARCHAR(100),                   -- Pseudonymized
    client_ip_hash VARCHAR(64),             -- Hashed for privacy

    -- Input / Output
    input_hash VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,        -- For dedup / verification
    input_features JSONB,                   -- Anonymized features
    output_prediction JSONB NOT NULL,
    confidence_score DECIMAL(5,4),

    -- Explainability
    feature_attributions JSONB,             -- SHAP values
    decision_factors JSONB,                 -- Top-N contributing factors

    -- Governance
    risk_level VARCHAR(20),
    human_review_required BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    human_reviewed BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    human_reviewer_id VARCHAR(100),
    human_review_decision VARCHAR(50),
    human_review_timestamp TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE,

    -- Compliance
    consent_verified BOOLEAN,
    data_retention_date DATE,
    regulatory_flags JSONB,

    -- System
    environment VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    region VARCHAR(50),
    instance_id VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE INDEX idx_model_version ON ai_decision_audit(model_id, model_version);
CREATE INDEX idx_created_at ON ai_decision_audit(created_at);
CREATE INDEX idx_trace_id ON ai_decision_audit(trace_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_human_review ON ai_decision_audit(human_review_required, human_reviewed);

-- Immutability trigger
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION block_audit_update() RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$
BEGIN
    RAISE EXCEPTION 'ai_decision_audit is append-only (row id=%)', OLD.id;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

CREATE TRIGGER no_update BEFORE UPDATE ON ai_decision_audit
    FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION block_audit_update();

CREATE TRIGGER no_delete BEFORE DELETE ON ai_decision_audit
    FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION block_audit_update();

-- Monthly partitions for retention management
CREATE TABLE ai_decision_audit_2025_01 PARTITION OF ai_decision_audit
    FOR VALUES FROM ('2025-01-01') TO ('2025-02-01');
]]></code>
    </section>

