    </see-also>

    <note>AI governance is not just compliance — it is a competitive advantage. Organizations with strong governance ship faster, with fewer audit surprises and more stakeholder trust. Scale investment to actual risk exposure, not regulatory checkbox compliance: high-risk systems (credit, healthcare, employment) require comprehensive audit trails and human oversight; lower-risk systems benefit from lighter governance. Every deployed model must have at minimum: documentation, performance monitoring, and a clear escalation procedure for performance degradation.</note>
  </content>
</methodology>
